query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('cs',
'gamedev',
'money',
'sharepoint',
'wordpress') AND t1.name IN ('2010',
'2013',
'custom-post-types',
'php',
'plugins',
'sharepoint-enterprise',
'sharepoint-online',
'sharepoint-server',
'united-states',
'unity')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 10
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Commentator',
'Custodian',
'Notable Question',
'Tumbleweed') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
